<div class="related_info">
  






  

  <h2>
    <span>内容简介</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>



<div class="indent" id="link-report">
    
      <div class="">
        <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>《爷爷变成了幽灵》以平淡的语气表达浓浓的祖孙之情。书中朴实、淡彩的图画，不但感受不到死亡的可怕，反而从中找到了渲泻感情的出口。在感动之余，我们能感受到的是更多的对亲情的怀念与感悟。</p></div>

      </div>
    

</div>

  
      

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img9.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/other/online-partner.36905.css">


  




<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/subject/authors_section.6022b.css">

<h2>
    
  

  <h2>
    <span>爷爷变成了幽灵的创作者</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


</h2>
<div class="indent">
    <p></p>
    <div id="authors" class="authors">
    <ul class="authors-list from-subject __oneline">
            
            <li class="author">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/1404034/" title="金·弗珀兹·艾克松">
                    <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/cuphead/book-static/pics/author-default-medium.png" alt="金·弗珀兹·艾克松" class="avatar">
                </a>
                <div class="info">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/1404034/" title="金·弗珀兹·艾克松" class="name">金·弗珀兹·艾克松</a>
                    <span class="role">作者</span>
                </div>
            </li>
             
            
            <li class="author">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4505767/" title="彭懿">
                    <img src="https://img2.doubanio.com/view/personage/raw/public/6a8a62b9aa542d37020a399059a25f02.jpg" alt="彭懿" class="avatar">
                </a>
                <div class="info">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/author/4505767/" title="彭懿" class="name">彭懿</a>
                    <span class="role">译者</span>
                </div>
            </li>
             
        <li class="author fake fake4"></li>
    </ul>
    </div>
